overview: The user initiated a project to enhance a Sleep Questionnaire
  Application by adding database functionality, an admin dashboard, and
  authentication. The agent evaluated the existing codebase, identified missing
  components, and developed a comprehensive plan. Key implementations included
  updating demographic data fields, creating a Prisma model for questionnaire
  responses, and developing API endpoints for data submission and CSV export. An
  admin dashboard with a login page was built to allow clients to view and
  download responses. Initially, a custom session-based authentication was
  implemented, but it was later simplified to leverage Next.js middleware for
  more streamlined route protection. The agent provided detailed setup
  instructions for NeonDB and guided the user through testing, identifying a
  minor issue with the "Pre-fill & Jump to Report" button not triggering data
  submission.
